1
00:00:04,061 --> 00:00:06,813
Trivikram Maharaj: In Brazil there was
a very intense experience.

2
00:00:06,813 --> 00:00:09,568
You know, I never more got that, like ...

3
00:00:09,568 --> 00:00:10,996
You know, someone …

4
00:00:10,996 --> 00:00:13,398
I’ve already read 
Chaitanya-charitamrita,

5
00:00:13,398 --> 00:00:15,445
and then you have, you know,
that was my feelings,

6
00:00:15,445 --> 00:00:18,781
maybe, most probably,
I was tripping out,

7
00:00:18,781 --> 00:00:24,579
but I mean, you know, “Someone from
Chaitanya-charitamrita is living there.”

8
00:00:24,657 --> 00:00:28,044
[“Krishna, What’s Wrong with You?”]

9
00:00:28,089 --> 00:00:30,083
Goswami Maharaj:
As Srila Gurudev. Yes, right.

10
00:00:30,083 --> 00:00:33,193
(TM): Someone is coming 
from Chaitanya-chairtamrita and manifesting.

11
00:00:33,193 --> 00:00:37,440
(GM): That type of personality 
has stepped out of the pages in your life.

12
00:00:37,440 --> 00:00:41,909
(TM): Yes. And living there in
the ashram and doing his … lila.

13
00:00:41,909 --> 00:00:44,552
(GM): It is true! It works.
(TM): That was the feeling.

14
00:00:44,552 --> 00:00:47,413
And everybody had some feelings,
extraordinary feelings.

15
00:00:47,413 --> 00:00:51,341
And then the boy fell. 
That was the most …

16
00:00:51,341 --> 00:00:54,408
(GM): Yes. Was not that the day
when you give everything?

17
00:00:54,408 --> 00:00:56,138
Something happened.

18
00:00:56,138 --> 00:00:58,762
Do you know, Lalita?

19
00:01:00,002 --> 00:01:05,093
(GM): The baby, the boy
falls in the water and drowns.

20
00:01:06,125 --> 00:01:11,501
Gurudev told me 
that he said about you [Trivikram Maharaj]

21
00:01:11,501 --> 00:01:18,468
“He has just given me everything, 
everyone has come here in joyful celebration.”

22
00:01:18,468 --> 00:01:22,769
And a little kid fell in a pond
and drowned.

23
00:01:22,769 --> 00:01:25,544
Died. He is dead.

24
00:01:25,544 --> 00:01:28,973
Like these little children we have here,
that’s why we should be careful.

25
00:01:28,973 --> 00:01:29,715
(TM): Completely careful.

26
00:01:29,715 --> 00:01:31,376
(GM): We are letting them play
and everything …

27
00:01:31,376 --> 00:01:32,756
That child fell in a pond,

28
00:01:32,756 --> 00:01:35,662
that is only this big,
and drowned.

29
00:01:35,662 --> 00:01:38,550
So there is a dead child 
laying there,

30
00:01:38,550 --> 00:01:40,642
and Gurudev …
You will tell what he told,

31
00:01:40,642 --> 00:01:42,947
but he told me, he said,

32
00:01:42,947 --> 00:01:47,040
“I said to Kṛṣṇa, 
‘What do I tell them now?

33
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:49,136
I don’t know what to say.

34
00:01:49,136 --> 00:01:50,957
He just gave everything,

35
00:01:50,957 --> 00:01:53,365
we are having a big celebration.

36
00:01:53,365 --> 00:01:56,043
What am I supposed to tell them?

37
00:01:56,043 --> 00:01:57,895
I do not know what to say.

38
00:01:57,895 --> 00:02:00,652
Please tell me what to say.’”

39
00:02:00,652 --> 00:02:03,049
And then Ananda …

40
00:02:03,049 --> 00:02:05,405
(TM): Yes, Ananya Bhakti,
she took the charge,

41
00:02:05,405 --> 00:02:08,873
because she is a dentist so she knows
all the first procedures.
 

42
00:02:08,873 --> 00:02:10,279
(GM): First aid.
(TM): Yes.

43
00:02:10,279 --> 00:02:12,199
Then she told the father.

44
00:02:12,199 --> 00:02:14,142
I was taking prasadam 
with the father;

45
00:02:14,142 --> 00:02:16,539
the father was the guy
who gave me the first book.

46
00:02:16,539 --> 00:02:18,110
Then she told him,

47
00:02:18,110 --> 00:02:24,308
“You must give a massage to his heart,
and I will breathe. Then we do five times.”

48
00:02:24,308 --> 00:02:25,560
You know, CPU or whatever …

49
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:27,333
(GM): CPR.
(TM): CPR.

50
00:02:27,333 --> 00:02:32,273
Then after some time Rohini started 
chanting the mantra with everybody

51
00:02:32,273 --> 00:02:35,197
“Hare Kṛṣṇa, Hare Kṛṣṇa,
Kṛṣṇa Kṛṣṇa, Hare Hare …”

52
00:02:35,197 --> 00:02:39,533
Then, after maybe four or five …

53
00:02:39,533 --> 00:02:40,363
(GM): Minutes?

54
00:02:40,363 --> 00:02:41,318
(TM): Breaths.

55
00:02:41,318 --> 00:02:44,165
The boy starts vomitting the water,

56
00:02:44,165 --> 00:02:47,103
coughing and putting the water out.

57
00:02:47,103 --> 00:02:49,103
And then Gurudev told us …

58
00:02:49,103 --> 00:02:53,226
At that time someone went to tell him,

59
00:02:53,226 --> 00:02:55,982
and he said Gurudev was very silent

60
00:02:55,982 --> 00:02:57,496
and then he prayed to the Lord,

61
00:02:57,496 --> 00:02:58,956
“Why are you doing that?”

62
00:02:58,956 --> 00:03:00,413
And then the boy came alive.

63
00:03:00,413 --> 00:03:02,103
And Gurudev always said,

64
00:03:02,103 --> 00:03:04,874
“Ananya Bhakti saved the boy.”

65
00:03:04,874 --> 00:03:07,936
(GM): Right. He is not taking the credit.

66
00:03:07,936 --> 00:03:13,142
Kṛṣṇa answered Gurudev’s prayer
is what happened.

67
00:03:13,144 --> 00:03:16,905
And later at … What’s her name?

68
00:03:16,905 --> 00:03:19,147
Cesar?

69
00:03:19,147 --> 00:03:21,236
(TM): Neza Caesar.
(GM): Neza Cesar.

70
00:03:21,236 --> 00:03:23,884
At her house, 
that program that evening,

71
00:03:23,884 --> 00:03:25,827
I see that boy again.

72
00:03:25,827 --> 00:03:27,285
When Bhuvana showing me

73
00:03:27,285 --> 00:03:32,064
how to put passion fruit
on chocolate icecream.

74
00:03:32,064 --> 00:03:33,549
He loved to eat.

75
00:03:33,549 --> 00:03:34,953
(TM): This is like his specialty.

76
00:03:34,953 --> 00:03:36,089
(GM): And that kid is …

77
00:03:36,089 --> 00:03:37,170
And they go,
“That’s the kid.”

78
00:03:37,170 --> 00:03:40,426
(TM): No brain damage
after fifteen minutes drowned.

79
00:03:40,426 --> 00:03:41,878
(GM): How old is he now?

80
00:03:41,878 --> 00:03:43,097
(TM): Oh, he may be now …

81
00:03:43,097 --> 00:03:45,987
(GM): Fifteen, seventeen years old, 
totally normal.

82
00:03:45,987 --> 00:03:47,895
It was a mi …

83
00:03:47,895 --> 00:03:50,896
It’s what they call “A Miracle”.

84
00:03:50,896 --> 00:03:57,184
But the miracle was Gurudev
not just going “Oh, my Lord.”

85
00:03:57,184 --> 00:03:59,556
Not like that, saying,
“What’s wrong with you?!

86
00:03:59,556 --> 00:04:02,156
Kṛṣṇa, what’s wrong with you?

87
00:04:02,156 --> 00:04:04,693
He just gave everything,
we are having a big celebration,

88
00:04:04,693 --> 00:04:10,202
what am I supposed to tell them now?
You tell me what would I do.”

89
00:04:10,423 --> 00:04:14,205
Devotee can express 
that kind of anger, loving anger,

90
00:04:14,205 --> 00:04:19,565
Kṛṣṇa likes that that His devotee
can say something like that.

91
00:04:19,575 --> 00:04:20,932
And then Kṛṣṇa says …

92
00:04:20,932 --> 00:04:22,993
Balaram says [to Kṛṣṇa].

93
00:04:22,993 --> 00:04:26,545
When they are all lying fainted
on the banks of Jamuna

94
00:04:26,545 --> 00:04:29,658
He [Balaram] goes,
“These are not Ayodhya monkeys!

95
00:04:29,924 --> 00:04:31,860
These are not Vaikuntha people!

96
00:04:31,860 --> 00:04:35,877
These are Your beloved devotees
in Vrindavan!

97
00:04:35,877 --> 00:04:37,647
Stop this play!

98
00:04:37,647 --> 00:04:40,254
You are breaking their hearts!”

99
00:04:40,254 --> 00:04:42,324
And then Kṛṣṇa
goes like “Alright”.

100
00:04:42,324 --> 00:04:44,197
[Laughing]

101
00:04:44,197 --> 00:04:47,603
And Viśvanāth says,
“Why does He do these things?

102
00:04:47,603 --> 00:04:50,766
Because He is 
bhava-grahi janardana,

103
00:04:50,766 --> 00:04:52,206
He is a bhava-eater.”

104
00:04:52,206 --> 00:04:56,463
And He knows, there is what’s regularly
going on in your heart,

105
00:04:56,463 --> 00:04:59,060
that taste … it’s also nice,

106
00:04:59,060 --> 00:05:02,030
but if He puts you 
in great difficulty,

107
00:05:02,035 --> 00:05:04,996
the heart will go 
to its deepest place

108
00:05:04,996 --> 00:05:09,022
and make an offering from there
that He can’t refuse.

109
00:05:09,032 --> 00:05:11,643
That’s why He does it.

110
00:05:11,902 --> 00:05:13,912
He is addicted to heart.

111
00:05:14,243 --> 00:05:15,855
Hare Kṛṣṇa!

